<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to WordWave!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6962AD, #7A81EB);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            width: 120px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px;
            color: #444;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6962AD, #7A81EB);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .social-links {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #6962AD;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to WordWave!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong>{{username}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for joining WordWave! Your account has been successfully created.</p>
            <p>With WordWave, you can:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Learn new vocabulary every day</li>
                <li>Track your learning progress</li>
                <li>Practice with interactive exercises</li>
                <li>Build your personal word collection</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Ready to start your language learning journey?</p>
            <center>
                <a href="https://wordwave-app.com/dashboard" class="button">Get Started Now</a>
            </center>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The WordWave Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent on {{date}}.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 WordWave. All rights reserved.</p>
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Twitter</a> |
                <a href="#">Facebook</a> |
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>